flowchart TD
    A["Command.move<br/>玩家或 WarCommandExecutor 生成"]:::command
    B["CommandValidator.validateMove"]:::rules
    C{"是否合法?"}:::decision
    R["CommandResult rejected<br/>state 不变"]:::stop
    M["CommandExecutor.executeMove<br/>更新 Division.coord / facing / hasActed"]:::rules
    O{"OccupationRules.canOccupy?<br/>可占、非己方控制、无其他单位<br/>neutral objective 可被地面移动夺取"}:::decision
    NO["只移动<br/>不改 controller"]:::state
    HC["目标 HexTile.controller = division.faction"]:::authority
    SA{"是否需要动态战区推进?<br/>占领 / 目标控制与 ROE hostile 分开"}:::decision
    ET["TheaterSystem.expandDynamicTheater<br/>只改目标 hex 的 hexToTheater"]:::authority
    AF["WarDeploymentManager.advanceHex<br/>只改目标 hex 的 hexToFrontZone"]:::authority
    SS["StrategicStateSynchronizer"]:::rules
    RO["RegionOccupationRules.aggregateControl<br/>从 hex controller 加权聚合 region controller"]:::derived
    TU["TheaterSystem.updateTheaters(force)<br/>刷新 ratio / unitIds / neighbor theaters"]:::derived
    FU["FrontLineManager.update<br/>按 dirty region 重新扫描动态 hex 接触"]:::derived
    DU["WarDeploymentManager.update<br/>刷新 FRONT / DEPTH / GARRISON"]:::derived
    UI["UI overlay / inspector / log 刷新"]:::ui

    A --> B --> C
    C -->|否| R
    C -->|是| M --> O
    O -->|否| NO --> UI
    O -->|是| HC --> SA
    SA -->|目标已属己方动态 theater| SS
    SA -->|其他 zone 或非本方控制 hex| ET --> AF --> SS
    SS --> RO --> TU --> FU --> DU --> UI

    WARN1["禁止：占一个 hex 就改整个 regionToTheater"]:::warn
    WARN2["禁止：只改 region controller 不改 hex controller"]:::warn
    ET -.守住.-> WARN1
    HC -.守住.-> WARN2

    classDef command fill:#fae8ff,stroke:#a21caf,color:#2a0a2f
    classDef rules fill:#ccfbf1,stroke:#0f766e,color:#042f2e
    classDef decision fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#ea580c,color:#1f1300
    classDef stop fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#b91c1c,color:#111827
    classDef state fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#1f143d
    classDef authority fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,color:#111827
    classDef derived fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#052e16
    classDef ui fill:#e5e7eb,stroke:#4b5563,color:#111827
    classDef warn fill:#ffedd5,stroke:#f97316,color:#431407
